title: After Win, Hochul Confronts Challenges and Some Second-Guessing
description: Gov. Kathy Hochul managed to repel late momentum by her Republican opponent, Lee Zeldin. Now she must govern over a fractured New York electorate.
dc:creator: Luis Ferré-Sadurní
media:description: Gov. Kathy Hochul on Tuesday became the first woman to be elected governor of New York.
